This is Perl module TheSchwartz::Plugin::Logger.

INSTALLATION

TheSchwartz::Plugin::Logger installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan TheSchwartz::Plugin::Logger

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

TheSchwartz::Plugin::Logger documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc TheSchwartz::Plugin::Logger

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

